----------------------------------------------------------------------
				   
			F  I  D  O  G  A  T  E
				 ----
	     Fidonet-Internet Gateway and Fidonet Tosser
				   
			  Version 4.0 alpha

----------------------------------------------------------------------

This is an experimental ALPHA release of the new FIDOGATE version
4.0. It is intended to be used by people already familiar with
FIDOGATE 3.9.7.

The documentation in doc/ is currently NOT up-to-date!!!

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Major changes in FIDOGATE 4.0:

* Areas in AREAS.BBS must now explicitly marked as passthru (dir entry
  must start with `#'), otherwise ftntoss will create packets for the
  own address as well.

* Gateway can now work under the same main address as the tosser
  (config.gate: Address == Uplink).

* A lot of new config options (see examples/...).

* If the KillXXXX options are not specified, ftntoss will put bad
  messages into packets in SPOOLDIR/toss/bad.

* File attach processing: option -F must be used with ftnpack.

* Dupe check: ftntoss now uses a MSGID history database if enabled.

* Tons of new config options! See examples/orodruin/
  examples/morannon/.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Needed:

-   GNU CC or ANSI C compiler
-   GNU make
-   GNU flex/bison or lex/yacc
-   Perl 4.036+

Compiling:

1.  Edit config.h
2.  Edit config.make
3.  Type "make depend"
4.  Type "make"

Installing:

1.  Type "make install-dirs" to create the necessary directories if
    needed
2.  Type "make install"

----------------------------------------------------------------------

There is a mailing list for FIDOGATE discussions and announcements:

    fgate-users@gondor.gun.de

Send mail to

    fgate-users-request@gondor.gun.de

for subscription.

